# --- Transcription ---
# video-use supports three backends. Set whichever key(s) you have.
# Only one is used per run; priority: ElevenLabs > OpenAI > local Whisper.

# ElevenLabs Scribe — best cut-point detection. ~$0.40 per 10 min audio.
# Get yours at https://elevenlabs.io/app/settings/api-keys
ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=

# OpenAI Whisper — accurate, lower cost; also Hyperframes' default backend.
# Also unlocks OpenAI image generation in compositions if needed.
# Get yours at https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# OPENAI_API_KEY=

# Local Whisper — free, runs on-device, no API key needed. Slower.
# Ask Claude Code to install it: "install local Whisper transcription"
# TRANSCRIPTION_BACKEND=local

# --- Optional ---
# Anthropic API — only needed if calling the API directly outside Claude Code.
# Claude Code reads its own credentials separately via `claude login`.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
